Deltathemes
------------
Collection of themes for Linux.
Licenced under GNU GPL v3.

Contents
-----------
Blu-Day
Blue theme for Openbox-3 window manager.
Based on GrayPhox by graphox graphoox.deviantart.com
Author: Juhani Numminen

Grazzy
White and green GTK 2.0 theme.
Author: Juhani Numminen

Hard-Pink
Pink, girly theme for Openbox-3 and GTK 2.0.
Author: Juhani Numminen

Nightly-Star
Openbox-3 theme made to match gtk2 theme newtonian flynn.
Based on Dark Star theme by na12.
Author: knembo2

Sleany
Theme for GTK 2.0.
Author: Juhani Numminen

Installing
-----------
There are several ways to install Deltathemes.

1) Use install.sh script. By default it installs to ~/.themes. See the
--help option.
 $ ./install.sh

2) Manual copying.
 $ cp Blu-Day/ Grazzy/ Hard-Pink/ Nightly-Star/ Sleany/ <DESTINATION DIR HERE>

3) Debian package for Ubuntu. See the web page
https://launchpad.net/~jsonic/+archive/ppa for more information.
